T1  - The governance of open science: A comparative analysis of two open science consortia
AU  - Abrams, Ellen
AU  - Leone, Paolo V.
AU  - Cambrosio, Alberto
AU  - Faraj, Samer
JO  - Research Policy
VL  - 54
IS  - 3
SP  - 105195
